data.description: This beautiful home is an absolute gem waiting to welcome its new owners! With its well-designed two-story layout, open floor plan, and four spacious bedrooms, it's nice for families seeking comfort and style. The 3.5 bathrooms provide convenience and luxury, with an exquisite master bathroom featuring an extra-large shower and separate tub. The first floor boasts a seamless flow between the formal living and dining rooms, a cozy family room complete with a gas fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring upgraded 42' cabinets, granite countertops, a generous island, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The second floor offers a master bedroom with a sitting room, creating a serene retreat within your own home. The upper deck above the screened rear porch provides a great view for relaxation and entertaining. Additional amenities include a convenient laundry room and a 2-car attached garage.  Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
